00:20:37,821 --> 00:20:39,238
- Come on, give me it, give!
- Oh, my God.

381
00:20:39,406 --> 00:20:40,906
- ROY: Is it loaded?
- This is my baby.

382
00:20:41,074 --> 00:20:43,617
- My baby? Oh, my God.
