441
00:22:57,669 --> 00:23:02,422
I just hope you're not starting to care
for him too much, in the wrong way.

442
00:23:03,341 --> 00:23:05,384
Oh, God, no.
I love Roy.

443
00:23:07,554 --> 00:23:11,056
Although it is interesting to be around
someone so complicated.

444
00:23:11,224 --> 00:23:13,767
I fear for him, I do.
I, you know...

445
00:23:13,935 --> 00:23:16,603
